  "version": "1.3.0-rc01",
  "releaseDate": "2024-01-10",
  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"1.3.0-rc01\" data-text=\"Version 1.3.0-rc01\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.3.0-rc01</h3>\n<p>January 10, 2024</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.wear.compose:compose-*:1.3.0-rc01</code> is released. <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/b76585a287cbcfdae38c3e16e5acbc6e26e808e2..37d04ed2f8dfcced119779f812301352786bc623/wear/compose\">Version 1.3.0-rc01 contains these commits.</a></p>\n<p><strong>Bug Fixes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>We have updated the <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">MaterialTheme</code> large shape to use a 26dp rounded corner radius and this will now be used by Chip and <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">ToggleChip</code>. This change is needed to support height adjustments when contents need extra height to accommodate large font sizes—otherwise, the existing stadium shape clips some text content.</p>\n\n<figure id=\"include-font-padding-true\">\n  <img src=\"/static/jetpack/androidx/images/ChipFullRoundedCornerTextClipping.svg\" width=\"50%\" alt=\"Text clipped on corners\">\n  <figcaption><b>Figure 1</b>: Text clipped on corners.</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n\n<figure id=\"include-font-padding-false\">\n  <img src=\"/static/jetpack/androidx/images/ChipLargeCornerNoTextClipping.svg\" width=\"50%\" alt=\"Text not clipped\">\n  <figcaption><b>Figure 2</b>: Text not clipped.</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n\n<p>This change may cause a breakage in screenshot tests.\n(<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/I2e6ae57e2c7f47521cf48d518fd9ff67e030f6da\">I2e6ae</a>)</p>\n</li>\n</ul>",
  "commitsUrl": "https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/b76585a287cbcfdae38c3e16e5acbc6e26e808e2..37d04ed2f8dfcced119779f812301352786bc623/wear/compose"
}